This file is the product frame: the direction every piece of development work
is checked against. It answers *why the product exists, for whom, what it
pursues, and what it deliberately does not*. It is a living state document —
when the scope shifts, this file changes **in the same change**, which routes
product decisions through the normal cycle (tier routing, review, decision
records). Keep it one page: a compass, not a spec. Features live in the
feature registry; individual decisions live in the decision records
(`docs/process/adr/`).

